{"tid":2004920,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警溫祖榮同佢女朋友，害死消防隊目","createTime":"2020-05-06T18:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T18:50:17.000Z","uid":274204,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41a4065317319078b536d2a88d21babc4f24079b","tid":2004920,"uid":274204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T18:36:50.000Z","msg":"只係因為一個勁高估自己能力，最後害死咗個消防隊目，拆散人哋家庭，搞到人哋要做孤兒寡婦，點解黑警咁黑心，夜晚能心安理得咁去瞓覺？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200506&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60909949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200506%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60909949&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=8bb6f6fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200506%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60909949&h=afd76306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200506&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60909949</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mx0fWrk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmx0fWrk.png&h=57a74cad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9bFjDEH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9bFjDEH.png&h=d7058c41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合庭上證供，現時駐守<span style=\"color: red;\">新界南機動部隊的34歲警員</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">溫祖榮</span></span>偕同女友行山，於2017年3月21日下午6時許，報警稱在吊手岩附近被困。邱少明於3月22日凌晨1時許到場增援，搜救至凌晨5時10分墮崖，消防員6分鐘後找到邱，邱當時沒有呼吸和脈搏，直至下午3時半由飛行服務隊送往沙田消防局，再轉往威爾斯親王醫院救治，同日下午4時17分宣告死亡。<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源（2019年4月）<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190403/s00001/1554264659730/%e6%b6%88%e9%98%b2%e7%b8%bd%e9%9a%8a%e7%9b%ae%e9%82%b1%e5%b0%91%e6%98%8e%e6%95%91%e5%9b%b0%e5%b1%b1%e5%ae%a2%e5%a2%ae%e6%96%83-%e8%a3%81%e5%ae%9a%e6%ad%bb%e6%96%bc%e6%84%8f%e5%a4%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.co